      • encode

        static byte[] encode​(byte[] password,
                     byte[] salt)
              throws NoSuchAlgorithmException
        Hashes the given password using the MD5 Crypt algorithm.
        Parameters:
        password - the password to be hashed
        salt - the salt, will be truncated to an array of 8 bytes if an array larger than 8 bytes is given
        Returns:
        a byte[] containing the hashed password
        Throws:
        NoSuchAlgorithmException - if a MessageDigest object that implements MD5 cannot be retrieved
